Marico Ltdhas informed BSE that the meeting of the Board of Directors of the Company is scheduled on 05/05/2026 ,inter alia, to consider and approve i. the Audited Standalone & Consolidated financial results of the Company for the quarter and financial year ended March 31, 2026; 
ii. take on record the Auditor's Report on Standalone & Consolidated financial results; and
iii. consider a proposal for recommendation of Final Equity Dividend, if any, ....
